<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٤٢٧٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَكْرٍ قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ مَهْدِيٍّ، عَنْ شُعْبَةَ، عَنِ الْحَكَمِ،<span class="c5"> وَحَمَّادٍ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُهُمَا عَنِ الِاجْتِمَاعِ عَشِيَّةَ عَرَفَةَ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَا:</span> <span class="c2">«مُحْدَثٌ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>